      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-3xl">Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Driven by a singular passion to see the next generation established in God.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        
         History Card 
        <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 flex flex-col">
            <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden relative">
                <%#= image_tag "/about_1.png", class: "w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500", alt: "History" %>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
                <h3 class="absolute bottom-3 left-4 text-lg font-bold text-white">Our History</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 flex-grow">
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                    Founded in 1992, TOM International began with a burden. From a small fellowship, we have grown into a multi-national ministry affecting thousands of lives across the continent.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 pt-0 mt-auto">
                 <span class="text-leaf-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide group-hover:underline">Read Story &rarr;</span>
            </div>
        </div>

         Mission Card 
        <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 flex flex-col">
            <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden relative">
                 <%#= image_tag "/about_2.png", class: "w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500", alt: "Mission" %>
