                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 pt-0 mt-auto">
                 <span class="text-leaf-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide group-hover:underline">Join Mission &rarr;</span>
            </div>
        </div>

         Vision Card 
         <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 flex flex-col">
            <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden relative">
                 <%#= image_tag "/about_3.png", class: "w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500", alt: "Vision" %>
                 <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent"></div>
                 <h3 class="absolute bottom-3 left-4 text-lg font-bold text-white">Our Vision</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5 flex-grow">
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                   A world where teenagers stand as pillars of truth in every sector of society. We envision young leaders transforming their communities and leading revivals.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="px-5 pb-5 pt-0 mt-auto">
                 <span class="text-leaf-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide group-hover:underline">See Future &rarr;</span>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>-->
    
  </div>

  <!-- Leadership Section (Simple Clean List) -->
  <div id="leadership" class="bg-stone-50 py-16 sm:py-20 border-t border-stone-100">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-3xl">Our Leadership</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">
            Guided by wisdom and driven by love for the next generation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <ul role="list" class="mx-auto mt-12 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-12 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
        <li>
            <!-- Card Style for Leader -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 text-center shadow-sm border border-stone-100/50">
                 <div class="mx-auto h-24 w-24 rounded-full bg-gray-50 overflow-hidden mb-4 border-2 border-white shadow-sm">
                    <!-- Placeholder avatar if no image -->
                    <svg class="h-full w-full text-gray-300" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M24 20.993V24H0v-2.996A14.977 14.977 0 0112.004 15c4.904 0 9.26 2.354 11.996 5.993zM16.002 8.999a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
                    </svg>
                 </div>
                 <h3 class="text-base font-bold leading-7 tracking-tight text-gray-900">Pastor Adetokunbo Emmanuel</h3>
                 <p class="text-xs font-medium leading-6 text-leaf-600 uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">International Director</p>
            </div>
        </li>
         <!-- Add more leaders here -->
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
